{"tid":460202,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]South Park: Phone destroyer 於11月9日係球上線","createTime":"2017-11-06T12:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T19:52:09.000Z","uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c37c1caad48453e646459d27cef154a30a8e167","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.images.southparkstudios.com/blogs/southparkstudios.com/files/2017/06/sp-phone-destroyer-blog.jpg?quality=0.8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.images.southparkstudios.com%2Fblogs%2Fsouthparkstudios.com%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F06%2Fsp-phone-destroyer-blog.jpg%3Fquality%3D0.8&h=93711cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://southparkphonedestroyer.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsouthparkphonedestroyer.com%2F&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1e53d7a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://southparkphonedestroyer.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n          由 Ubisoft 旗下 RedLynx 工作室與《南方四賤客》電視動畫原創作者 Trey Parker 及 Matt Stone 合作開發的《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂》，是一款結合了即時戰鬥與傳統的集換式卡片機制的手機遊戲，目前已於 Google Play 展開預先註冊，預估上線日期為 2017 年 11 月 9 日。<br />\n<br />\n　　《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂（South Park: Phone Destroyer）》將於 11 月 9 日在全球正式發佈，玩家如果現在參加預先註冊，就能在遊戲推出時取得可裝扮虛擬人偶的獨家「人熊豬」造型。<br />\n<br />\n　　官方表示，《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂》融合了經典的南方四賤客人物、緊張刺激的即時戰略、玩家對戰、原汁原味的南方四賤客幽默和卡牌收集要素，集結西部牛仔、巫師、改造人等等眾多勢力，組成終極隊伍，準備好打趴對手。<br />\n<br />\n　　遊戲中將包含經典角色另類新版本，例如「遠古屎蛋」、「改造人阿尼」、「客家忍者凱子」、「巫師王阿ㄆ一ㄚˇ」，還有其他更多角色，並且與 South Park Digital Studios 合作編劇，帶領玩家體驗無厘頭的單人遊戲劇情。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/154633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F3%2F154633.html&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=44222aff\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/154633.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ad42b33c68fbfcf2f5b01793866178a8608df7c","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"Gameplay<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wCz3slriANc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwCz3slriANc&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9301e5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wCz3slriANc</a>"},{"pid":"8ce40f20d20223e83437df7d9afe966338d835b6","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648ecd85e53c005b34d46c0e0a67f60ede5d7fd6","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee056b5e952cacd11194ecb51608894811335575","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87182eef40eae6ddbeef944d15907ac2890ad23e","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114e564d43ae7c69bb05bf7253ffda83eacf227e","tid":460202,"uid":35585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3be80c87d372ec362fdeb6cab5f10c597c49bde","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc45b9359073bdcb753d51ded80e1d599ad8866","tid":460202,"uid":91195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"睇完gameplay都唔明玩d乜?<br />\n點先算贏"},{"pid":"60d0a7ef720b1cfd03e8d4e96284413a027f6088","tid":460202,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor